WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.870 align:middle line:90%


00:00:00.870 --> 00:00:04.200 align:middle line:84%
>> A groundbreaking new study
suggests that commonly used

00:00:04.200 --> 00:00:07.890 align:middle line:84%
anti-inflammatory drugs
and steroids may cause pain

00:00:07.890 --> 00:00:09.570 align:middle line:90%
to become chronic.

00:00:09.570 --> 00:00:11.730 align:middle line:84%
Could this lead to
a dramatic paradigm

00:00:11.730 --> 00:00:15.630 align:middle line:84%
shift in how pain is
managed and prevented?

00:00:15.630 --> 00:00:17.865 align:middle line:90%
This is a Gaia News Breakdown.

00:00:17.865 --> 00:00:21.204 align:middle line:90%
